# Components and Interactions Rule

Every interactive component must feel polished, clear and usable.

Add interaction states only where they improve usability.

Do not over-animate.

## Components Requiring States

Add states for:

- primary buttons;
- secondary buttons if present;
- input fields;
- password visibility button;
- links;
- checkboxes;
- clickable badges;
- tabs;
- progress steps if interactive.

## Required States

Each relevant component must support:

- default;
- hover;
- focus-visible;
- active;
- disabled if applicable;
- loading if applicable;
- error if applicable.

## Inputs

Inputs must include:

- visible label;
- placeholder;
- left icon if shown in reference;
- dark background;
- subtle border;
- hover border;
- focus glow;
- error style;
- disabled style;
- dark autofill handling.

Example:

```css
.auth-input {
  height: 60px;
  border-radius: 13px;
  border: 1px solid var(--auth-input-border);
  background: var(--auth-input-bg);
  color: var(--auth-text-primary);
  padding: 0 48px 0 56px;
  outline: none;
  transition:
    border-color var(--auth-transition-base),
    box-shadow var(--auth-transition-base),
    background var(--auth-transition-base);
}

.auth-input:hover {
  border-color: var(--auth-input-border-hover);
}

.auth-input:focus {
  border-color: var(--auth-input-border-focus);
  box-shadow:
    0 0 0 4px rgba(91, 124, 255, 0.14),
    0 0 28px rgba(91, 124, 255, 0.18);
}

input:-webkit-autofill {
  -webkit-text-fill-color: var(--auth-text-primary);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1000px rgba(7, 11, 22, 0.96) inset;
  caret-color: var(--auth-text-primary);
}
```

## Buttons

Primary buttons must have:

- blue / periwinkle / violet gradient;
- white text;
- subtle shadow;
- hover lift;
- active press;
- disabled state;
- loading state if async action exists.

Example:

```css
.primary-button {
  height: 62px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 13px;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  font-weight: 700;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5F83FF 0%, #3F6BFF 52%, #695CFF 100%);
  box-shadow:
    0 16px 32px rgba(63, 107, 255, 0.28),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition:
    transform 160ms ease,
    box-shadow 180ms ease,
    filter 180ms ease;
}

.primary-button:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  filter: brightness(1.05);
}

.primary-button:active {
  transform: translateY(0);
  filter: brightness(0.98);
}

.primary-button:disabled {
  opacity: 0.58;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  transform: none;
  box-shadow: none;
}
```

## Links

Links must have:

- accent color;
- hover color;
- focus-visible outline;
- no layout jump.

## Icons

Use one icon style only.

Recommended:

- Lucide;
- Heroicons outline;
- or custom SVGs.

Do not mix inconsistent icon libraries.

Required icons:

- envelope;
- lock;
- eye;
- eye-off;
- optional sparkle/star.

## Motion

Use subtle motion:

- button hover lift;
- input focus glow;
- link color transition;
- checkbox check animation;
- card entrance only if it does not distract.

Respect reduced motion:

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.001ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.001ms !important;
    scroll-behavior: auto !important;
  }
}
```
